---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="The story behind Lightforged Creations — where cosmic inspiration meets artisan craftsmanship.">
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12">
        <p class="text-gold-300/80 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sm font-medium mb-4">Our Story</p>
        <h1 class="mb-8">
            <span class="text-gradient-gold">About Lightforged Creations</span>
        </h1>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-star-white/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
                Lightforged Creations was born from a fascination with the cosmos and a deep respect for the
                art of handcraft. We believe that the same forces that shape stars and forge elements in the
                hearts of supernovae can inspire beauty here on Earth.
            </p>
            <p>
                Every piece we create is a dialogue between the celestial and the tangible — between the
                vastness of space and the intimacy of something you can hold in your hands. Our workshop
                is where cosmic inspiration meets the anvil, where stardust meets skilled hands.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <section class="py-8">
        <h2 class="mb-10">
            <span class="text-gradient-gold">Our Values</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="cosmic-card">
                <h3 class="text-gold-300 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold">Craftsmanship First</h3>
                <p class="text-star-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                    Every creation passes through our hands multiple times. We never rush the process —
                    great work takes the time it needs, just as stars take millennia to form.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="cosmic-card">
                <h3 class="text-gold-300 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold">Cosmic Inspiration</h3>
                <p class="text-star-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                    The textures of nebulae, the geometry of crystal structures, the raw power of solar
                    flares — the universe is our endless wellspring of creative vision.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="cosmic-card">
                <h3 class="text-gold-300 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold">Unique by Nature</h3>
                <p class="text-star-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                    No two pieces are identical, just as no two stars are the same. We embrace the
                    variations that make each creation genuinely one-of-a-kind.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="cosmic-card">
                <h3 class="text-gold-300 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold">Sustainable Practice</h3>
                <p class="text-star-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                    We source our materials responsibly and minimize waste in our process. The cosmos
                    gave us this planet — we intend to take care of it.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12">
        <div class="cosmic-card max-w-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cosmic-700/80 to-cosmic-600/40 text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4">
                <span class="text-gradient-gold">Let's Create Something Together</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-star-white/70 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
                Have a custom piece in mind? We love collaborating on unique commissions that
                push the boundaries of craft and imagination.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start a Conversation</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
